#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.equal.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.equal"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.equal.equal:1 of
msgid "Return (x1 == x2) element-wise."
msgstr "逐元素返回(x1 == x2)的结果。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.equal.equal of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.equal.equal:3
#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.equal.equal:5 of
msgid "Input tensors of the same shape."
msgstr "形状相同的输入张量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.equal.equal:7 of
msgid ""
"A location into which the result is stored. If provided, it must have a "
"shape that the inputs broadcast to. If not provided or `None`, a freshly-"
"allocated array is returned. A tuple (possible only as a keyword "
"argument) must have length equal to the number of outputs."
msgstr ""
"用于存储结果的位置。如果提供，其形状必须可以广播到输入形状。如果未提供或"
"为 `None`，则返回一个新分配的数组。元组（仅可作为关键字参数）的长度必须"
"等于输出的数量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.equal.equal:12 of
msgid ""
"Values of True indicate to calculate the ufunc at that position, values "
"of False indicate to leave the value in the output alone."
msgstr "值为 True 表示在该位置计算ufunc，值为 False 表示保留输出中的原值。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.equal.equal:15 of
msgid ""
"For other keyword-only arguments, see the :ref:`ufunc docs "
"<ufuncs.kwargs>`."
msgstr "对于其他仅限关键字的参数，请参见 :ref:`ufunc 文档 <ufuncs.kwargs>`。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.equal.equal of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.equal.equal:18 of
msgid ""
"**out** -- Output tensor of bools, or a single bool if x1 and x2 are "
"scalars."
msgstr "**out** -- 布尔值的输出张量，如果x1和x2是标量，则返回单个布尔值。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.equal.equal of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.equal.equal:21 of
msgid ""
":py:obj:`not_equal`, :py:obj:`greater_equal`, :py:obj:`less_equal`, "
":py:obj:`greater`, :py:obj:`less`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.equal.equal:24 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.equal.equal:30 of
msgid ""
"What is compared are values, not types. So an int (1) and a tensor of "
"length one can evaluate as True:"
msgstr ""
"比较的是值，而不是类型。因此，一个整数(1)和一个长度为一的张量可以计算为"
"True："

